%hive

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS campaign_tables (
    validation_number STRING,
    id_campaign STRING,
    type_campaign STRING,
    days_valid STRING,
    data_campaign STRING,
    channel STRING,
    return_status STRING,
    return_date STRING,
    client_id STRING
)
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED
FIELDS TERMINATED BY ','
STORED AS TEXTFILE

%hive

LOAD DATA INPATH 's3a://tarefa1/campaigns_2023_hist.csv' 
INTO TABLE campaign_tables

paragraphs.text:
%hive

CREATE TABLE tabela_total_acessos AS
SELECT 
    id_campaign, 
    COUNT(client_id) AS total_acessos
FROM 
    campaign_tables
WHERE 
    from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(data_campaign, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss'), 'yyyy-MM-dd') >= '2023-01-01' 
    AND from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(data_campaign, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss'), 'yyyy-MM-dd') <= '2023-12-31'
GROUP BY 
    id_campaign

%hive

SELECT 
    tta.id_campaign,
    COUNT(ct.client_id) AS total_acessos,
    AVG(total_acessos) AS media_acessos
FROM 
    campaign_tables ct
LEFT JOIN 
    tabela_total_acessos tta
ON 
    tta.id_campaign = ct.id_campaign
GROUP BY 
    tta.id_campaign

paragraphs.text:
%hive

SELECT 
    id_campaign, 
    ano, 
    mes, 
    AVG(total_acessos) AS media_acessos
FROM 
    (
        SELECT 
            ct.id_campaign,
            YEAR(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(ct.data_campaign, 'yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm:ss'))) AS ano,
            MONTH(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(ct.data_campaign, 'yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm:ss'))) AS mes,
            COUNT(ct.client_id) AS total_acessos
        FROM 
            campaign_tables ct
        GROUP BY 
            ct.id_campaign,
            YEAR(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(ct.data_campaign, 'yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm:ss'))),
            MONTH(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(ct.data_campaign, 'yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm:ss')))
    ) AS acessos_mensais
GROUP BY 
    id_campaign, 
    ano, 
    mes
ORDER BY 
    id_campaign, 
    ano, 
    mes
